description: This source file contains unit tests for the UserSettings plugin, specifically testing various getter and setter methods related to user preferences such as audio description, language settings, captions, content pin, and migration states. It uses Google Test and Google Mock frameworks to mock dependencies and verify expected behaviors.

classes.name: UserSettingsTest
classes.description: A test fixture class that sets up the environment for testing UserSettings plugin methods, including mock dependencies and common initialization and cleanup procedures.
